sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Changes Webview
participant Router as ChangesMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as ChangesMutationUseCase
participant Worktree as Worktree implements WorktreeOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Select files and click Stage
App->>Router: changes/stagePaths(worktreeLocator, paths, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: stage(Worktree, paths, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: stage(paths, signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: stage(executionContext, paths, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: stage(executionContext, paths, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: success
Runtime-->>Worktree: success
Worktree-->>UseCase: success
UseCase-->>Router: success
Router-->>App: changes/stagePathsResponse(requestId)
Router-->>App: changes/refreshRequested

User->>App: Enter commit message and commit
App->>Router: changes/commit(worktreeLocator, message, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: commit(Worktree, message, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: commit(message, signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: commit(executionContext, message, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: commit(executionContext, message, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: success
Runtime-->>Worktree: success
Worktree-->>UseCase: success
UseCase-->>Router: success
Router-->>App: changes/commitResponse(requestId)
Router-->>App: changes/refreshRequested
